.TH "sdw_acquire_bus_lock" 9 "sdw_acquire_bus_lock" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
sdw_acquire_bus_lock \- Acquire bus lock for all Master runtime(s)
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" sdw_acquire_bus_lock
.BI "(struct sdw_stream_runtime *stream "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "stream" 12
SoundWire stream
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Acquire bus_lock for each of the master runtime(m_rt) part of this
stream to reconfigure the bus.
.SH "NOTE"
This function is called from SoundWire stream ops and is
expected that a global lock is held before acquiring bus_lock.
